While writing my review, I took two geeky detours: estimating how much time, exactly, it had taken me to read through _Umineko_; and how long is _Umineko_ compared to other works known for being incredibly long like Robert Jordan's _[The Wheel of Time](!Wikipedia)_ (which I have also read)?

